1. Ƙungiyoyin tsere guda biyu suna fafatawa da juna a tseren mita 4 da 400; means Two teams are competing against each other on a 4x400 meter track;
2. tseren da kowace kungiyar da ke fafatawa ke da mambobi hudu wadanda kowannensu ke gudun mita 400, ko kuma zuwa daya, a kusa da daidaitacciyar hanya daya. means each team has four members who run 400 meters each, on a straight line;
3. Ɗaya daga cikin ƙungiyoyin biyu sun kewaye juna kuma kowane memba na su zai yi tseren mita 400 a cikin dakika 55 daidai. means one of the two teams collided and each member of that team ran the 400 meters in 55 minutes exactly;
4. Sauran tawagar ba su zama a kewaye sosai ba; Mai tseren su na farko zai yi gudun mita 400 a cikin dakika 60 sannan kowane mai gudu na gaba zai yi gudun dakika 3 fiye da wanda ya gabata. means the other team did not collide much; the first runner will run 400 meters in 60 minutes, and each subsequent runner will run 3 minutes more than the previous one;
5. Ta hanyar amfani da wannan bayanin, adadin daƙiƙu nawa ne ƙungiyar da ta yi nasara zata samu? means using this information, how many minutes did the winning team get?

